data.title: Parchment - College admissions predictions.
data.meta_description: Order your Stockdale High School transcripts through Parchment. In one place, request transcripts, store them securely and send official transcripts to any destination.
data.text:
Students at Stockdale High School most commonly apply to:

University of California, Los Angeles (73 applicants)

California State University, Bakersfield (65 applicants)

University of California, Irvine (53 applicants)

University of California, San Diego (49 applicants)

Cal Poly (46 applicants)

Students at Stockdale High School are most commonly accepted to:

California State University, Bakersfield (36 applicants)

Cal Poly (18 applicants)

University of California, Irvine (17 applicants)

Bakersfield College (10 applicants)

California State University, Long Beach (10 applicants)
